title: Sports Briefing | Tennis: Kuznetsova Takes the Kremlin Cup
text:
Published By: NYTimes Tennis - Yesterday 
Svetlana Kuznetsova swept aside a tired Anastasia Pavlyuchenkova, 6-2, 6-1, to win the Kremlin Cup in Moscow....
